### Install a model from HF
POST http://localhost:7878/extensions/local-llm/models HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "huggingface",
  "repo_id": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct-GGUF",
  "revision": "main",
  "files": ["qwen2.5-7b-instruct-q4_k_m.gguf"],
  "display_name": "Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct (Q4_K_M)"
}

### Response 202 (task accepted, progress streams over event bus)
HTTP/1.1 202 Accepted
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {
    "task_id": "dl_9f3a1c2e",
    "model_install_id": "mi_7c4b2d10",
    "routed_backend": "llamacpp",
    "routing_signal": "gguf",
    "progress_channel": "extension:local-llm:model:progress",
    "cancel_endpoint": "/extensions/local-llm/models/tasks/dl_9f3a1c2e/cancel"
  },
  "error": null
}

### Response 409 — no compatible backend
HTTP/1.1 409 Conflict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "NO_COMPATIBLE_BACKEND",
    "message": "This model requires TensorRT-LLM. TensorRT-LLM is not installed on this host.",
    "resolution_hint": "Install TensorRT-LLM runtime from the Backends panel."
  }
}

### Response 422 — checksum mismatch discovered mid-install (delivered via progress channel)
# Never persisted as an installed model; task transitions to state=failed.
